# Frontend Environment Variables

## For Vercel Deployment

Add this to your frontend project on Vercel:

```
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.vercel.app/api
```

**Steps:**
1. Deploy backend first and copy the URL
2. Go to frontend project on Vercel
3. Settings â†’ Environment Variables
4. Name: `VITE_API_URL`
5. Value: `https://your-backend-url.vercel.app/api`
6. Click Add
7. Redeploy frontend

## For Local Development

Create a `.env` file in the `client` folder:

```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
```

**Note:** Vite requires environment variables to start with `VITE_`
